              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Three delta E-E spectrometers with",
                "silicon E detectors with 1 mm thickness, delta E",
                "detector in two of them was an ionization chamber, in",
                "the third spectrometer delta E detector was a silicon",
                "detector 67 mu-m thick. Flowing argon was used as the",
                "working gas in the ionization chamber. The energy loss",
                "of the ions in the ionization chamber corresponded to",
                "that deposited in an approximately 15 mu-m thick",
                "silicon detector."
              ]
